'''海莉·史坦菲德'''（英語：{{lang|en|Hailee Steinfeld}}，{{bd|1996年|12月11日}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MSfjCG4V2GM&t=372s|title=Hailee Steinfeld Answers the Web's Most Searched Questions {{!}} WIRED|website=YouTube}}</ref><ref name="BackStage">{{cite news |url=http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/a-girl-with-grit-1004134005.story |title=A Girl With 'Grit' |last=Riley |first=Jenelle |newspaper=[[Backstage_(magazine)|Backstage]] |date=December 13, 2010 |access-date=December 20, 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101223065112/http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/a-girl-with-grit-1004134005.story |archive-date=December 23, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>），是一名[[美國|美國]][[女演員|女演員]]及[[歌手|歌手]]。於[[柯恩兄弟|柯恩兄弟]]2010年執導的改編電影《[[真實的勇氣|真實的勇氣]]》中飾演「Mattie Ross」，憑此片獲提名[[第83届奥斯卡金像奖|第83届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角]]<ref name="abc101209"/>、[[美国演员工会奖最佳女配角|美国演员工会奖最佳女配角]]與[[英國電影學院獎最佳女主角|英國電影學院獎最佳女主角]]提名。

==早年==
史坦菲德出生於洛杉磯的{{link-en|塔扎納 (洛杉磯)|Tarzana, Los Angeles|塔扎納}}，室內設計師崔莉（舊姓杜馬辛）與個人健身教練彼得·史坦菲德的女兒<ref name=elolfoweyli>{{Cite news|last=Strauss|first=Bob|coauthors=|title=Thousand Oaks teen Hailee Steinfeld earns nods for big role in 'True Grit'|pages=|publisher=Daily News of Los Angeles|date=2010-12-18|url=http://www.dailynews.com/news/ci_16894415|accessdate=2011-01-07|archive-date=2012-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120912132230/http://www.dailynews.com/news/ci_16894415|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>http://blogs.laforward.org/2011/02/25/entertainment/hailee-steinfelds-true-colors/# {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727012149/http://blogs.laforward.org/2011/02/25/entertainment/hailee-steinfelds-true-colors/ |date=2011-07-27 }}</ref>。她有一個哥哥葛里芬<ref name=elolfoweyli/>，一個同為健身教練的叔叔{{link-en|傑克·史坦菲德|Jake Steinfeld}}<ref name=egaca>{{Cite news|last=Riley|first=Jenelle|coauthors=|title=A Girl With 'Grit'|pages=|publisher=Back Stage|date=2010-12-13|url=http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/a-girl-with-grit-1004134005.story|accessdate=2010-12-20|archive-date=2011-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110113091147/http://www.backstage.com/bso/news-and-features-features/a-girl-with-grit-1004134005.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Philip|last=Berk|url=https://www.star2.com/people/2017/01/12/this-actress-is-destined-for-greatness/|title=This actress is destined for greatness|work=Star2-com|date=January 12, 2017|accessdate=April 26, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427050349/https://www.star2.com/people/2017/01/12/this-actress-is-destined-for-greatness/|archive-date=2018-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Gil|last=Tanenbaum|url=http://jewishbusinessnews.com/2015/01/11/hailee-steinfeld-to-star-in-carrie-pilby/|title=Hailee Steinfeld To Star In Carrie Pilby|work=Jewish Business News|date=January 11, 2015|accessdate=April 26, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427045225/http://jewishbusinessnews.com/2015/01/11/hailee-steinfeld-to-star-in-carrie-pilby/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。母親有英國、[[非洲裔美國人|非洲裔美國人]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]與德國血統<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2794962/bio|title=Hailee Steinfeld - Biography|work=IMDb|access-date=2018-05-08|archive-date=2018-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327022949/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2794962/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Paolo|last=Abad|url=https://www.rappler.com/entertainment/music/128483-hailee-steinfeld-filipino-roots-interview-pitch-perfect|title=WATCH: Hailee Steinfeld on connecting with her Filipino roots|work=Rappler|date=April 6, 2016|accessdate=April 26, 2018|archive-date=2018-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427115900/https://www.rappler.com/entertainment/music/128483-hailee-steinfeld-filipino-roots-interview-pitch-perfect|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rerihet/><ref name=airefoylwh>{{Cite news|last=Bloom|first=Nate|coauthors=|title=On his own ‘Terms’?, Coen brothers get gritty, Kennedy Center honors, Paltrow, Midler on tap|pages=|publisher=The Jewish News Weekly of Northern California|date=2010-12-16|url=http://www.jweekly.com/article/full/60238/on-his-own-terms-coen-brothers-get-gritty-kennedy-center-honors-paltrow-mid/|accessdate=2010-12-20|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192009/http://www.jweekly.com/article/full/60238/on-his-own-terms-coen-brothers-get-gritty-kennedy-center-honors-paltrow-mid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。施丹菲先後在[[阿古拉丘_(加州)|阿古拉丘]]、[[紹曾德奧克斯_(加利福尼亞州)|-{zh-hans:绍曾德奥克斯;zh-hk:紹曾德奧克斯;zh-tw:千橡;}-]]長大<ref name=elolfoweyli/><ref name=radiofree/>，就讀亞松森信義學校、科內霍小學與{{link-en|科利訥中學|Colina Middle School}}<ref name=elcai>{{Cite news|last=Lindell|first=Karen|coauthors=|title=Ventura County Star, Calif., Karen Lindell column|pages=|publisher=California Chronicle|date=2010-12-24|url=http://www.californiachronicle.com/articles/yb/153845759|accessdate=2011-01-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120182443/http://www.californiachronicle.com/articles/yb/153845759|archivedate=2011-01-20}}</ref>。2008年起[[在家自學|在家自學]]<ref name=elcai/>。

==演員生涯==
她在8歲展開演藝生涯<ref name=radiofree>{{Cite news|last=Lee|first=Michael|coauthors=|title=Hailee Steinfeld on 'True Grit'|pages=|publisher=RadioFree.com|date=2010-12-09|url=http://www.radiofree.com/profiles/hailee_steinfeld/interview01.shtml|accessdate=2011-01-10|archive-date=2011-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120020707/http://www.radiofree.com/profiles/hailee_steinfeld/interview01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最後開始在許多以青年為導向的電影與劇集中擔任配角，並在{{link-en|K-Mart|Kmart}}商業廣告中出現。2011年1月16日，她與[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]在2011年金球獎上宣布最佳動畫獎提名人與獲獎者。

2011年1月25日，她獲得[[第83届奥斯卡金像奖|第83届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角獎]]提名。<ref name="bbc110125">{{cite news |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |title=Oscar nominations 2011 in full |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12278412 |date=January 25, 2011 |accessdate=January 25, 2011 |archive-date=2013-07-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HvPYvXhF?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12278412 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

